data.name: Git bob
data.description: My own custom version of git with functionalities like commit, stash, fetch etc. It is built with golang and is a cli tool that you could use instead of git (not recommended). It is missing some features like remote, git add(its auto) etc but it works.

data.name: React drag selection
data.description: A react library for drag to select--which is better than 70% of the alternatives. With just a classname and a react hook, you can add drag to select functionality to your react app.

data.name: Quantum computing programming language
data.description: A custom programming language for quantum computing. It is built with typescript and using mathematical methods and quantum computing concepts, makes programming quantum computers easy.

data.name: WhatsApp SMS Bot
data.description: A whatsapp bot that listens to a whatsapp group for messages, filters and formats the message and then posts the correct messages on an app, via SMS, Facebook and Twitter. It was built as part of a mobile app project for a church.

data.name: Bills Padi
data.description: A mobile app calles bills padi that helps users to be able to pay bills using loans. They could pay their airtime, data, nepa bills etc all with loans.
